* World e-Gov Forum
* e-forum Association dedicated to analysing the future needs of eGovernment in Europe
* Internet Society Organization home for the groups responsible for Internet infrastructure standards, including the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF) and the Internet Architecture Board (IAB).</text><links>
